Date: Wed, 26 Nov 2025 11:23:40 +0100
Subject: a11y: Report QQuickApplicationWindow locale

Similar to the support for QQuickControl introduced in
245f4d1d8b71375ff8900a53b876fdcf2c85c422, this adds support for the
locale set in QQuickApplicationWindow for the a11y layer.

Task-number: QTBUG-141701
Pick-to: 6.11
Change-Id: I258dc8ad022c9a998d5441c25cde49a1e7c32d16
Reviewed-by: Michael Weghorn <m.weghorn@posteo.de>
(Cherry-picked from commit 18de5bc509c673c16a323b18252b4be53addfe30)
---
 src/quicktemplates/CMakeLists.txt             |  1 +
 .../qaccessiblequickapplicationwindow.cpp     | 43 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../qaccessiblequickapplicationwindow_p.h     | 44 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../qtquicktemplates2global.cpp               |  3 ++
 4 files changed, 91 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 src/quicktemplates/accessible/qaccessiblequickapplicationwindow.cpp
 create mode 100644 src/quicktemplates/accessible/qaccessiblequickapplicationwindow_p.h

